com.orchestranetworks.ui

Class UICSSClasses.TABLE

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.orchestranetworks.ui.UICSSClasses.TABLE
  • Enclosing class:
    UICSSClasses

    public static final class UICSSClasses.TABLE
extends Object
    For basic tables (<table>, <tr>, <th> and <td> containing data).

    Attention: If a table is nested inside a basic table, the style will be inherited.
